results.description_highlighted: ...Star Wars Celebration Anaheim is over. Tricia Barr and Sarah Woloski bring the fun to you....
results.description_original:
Star Wars Celebration Anaheim is over. Tricia Barr and Sarah Woloski bring the fun to you. From the Obi-Wan Kenobi premiere to the surprising Tales of the Jedi panel, we share what excited us at the convention. There is a lot to look forward to in 2022 and beyond.

Related:

  • Episode 22.9: Animation is Art
  • Tales of the Jedi Panel via Skywalking Through Neverland
  • Tricia Barr discusses Jaina Solo on Tarkin's Top Shelf
  • Ahsoka Tano panel at Star Wars Celebration via Tarkin's Top Shelf
  • Fangirls Going Rogue Instagram Story from The Mandalorian Experience
  • Video of the Grogu and Bantha puppets at The Mandalorian Experience
  • Hyperspace Theories Obi-Wan Kenobi Storytelling Breakdown
  • Skywalking Through Neverland Day 1 recap
  • Ashley Eckstein and Matt Lanter Q & A from Exclusive Breakfast

BE SURE TO CHECK OUT OUR INTERVIEWS WITH HAYDEN CHRISTENSEN, EWAN MCGREGOR, MOSES INGRAM, AND DEBORAH CHOW!!
